## 🎯 Overview

**DEWS (Digital Executive Welfare System)** is a comprehensive loan and fund management platform designed for organizations, cooperatives, and financial institutions. The CEO Dashboard provides real-time insights into financial operations, member activities, loan performance, and inventory management.

### Key Highlights

- 📊 **Real-time Analytics** — Live KPI tracking with auto-refresh
- 💰 **Financial Intelligence** — Comprehensive income/expense tracking
- 👥 **Member Management** — Active/inactive member oversight
- 🏦 **Loan Tracking** — Outstanding balances, repayment schedules
- 📈 **Interactive Charts** — Visual trends with drill-down capability
- 📦 **Inventory Control** — Stock levels with low-stock alerts
- 📱 **Fully Responsive** — Desktop, tablet, and mobile optimized
- 🔒 **Secure Access** — Role-based authentication (AppGini compatible)

---

## ✨ Features

### 1️⃣ **Fund Overview Dashboard**

<table>
<tr>
<td width="50%">

**Real-time KPIs**
- Total Loan Fund Balance
- Active Loans (count + amount)
- Outstanding Due Amount
- Total Repayments Collected
- Active/Inactive Member Count
- Year-over-Year Member Fees

</td>
<td width="50%">

**Visual Indicators**
- Color-coded metrics (Green/Red/Blue/Orange)
- Trend badges (↑/↓ percentage changes)
- Progress bars for goals
- Status pills for quick insights

</td>
</tr>
</table>

### 2️⃣ **Financial Analytics**

- **Member Fees Tracking**
  - Current vs. Previous Year comparison
  - Monthly breakdown (Jan–Dec)
  - Unpaid fees identification
  
- **Income Management**
  - Other income by type (grouped)
  - Bank deposits by institution
  - Repayment collections (installment + interest + fees)

- **Expense Monitoring**
  - Bank withdrawals tracking
  - Year-over-year trends
  - Net change calculations

### 3️⃣ **Loan Analytics**

- **Member Loan Balances**
  - Unbalanced loan applications
  - Outstanding amounts per member
  - Payment progress bars
  - Overdue loan alerts

- **Repayment Tracking**
  - Recent payment history (last 20 transactions)
  - Payment type breakdown (installment/interest/fees)
  - Status monitoring (Active/Closed)

### 4️⃣ **Interactive Charts**

| Chart Type | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| 📊 **Bar Chart** | Monthly Member Fees Collection |
| 📈 **Line Chart** | Loan vs Repayment Trend |
| 📊 **Grouped Bar** | Bank Deposits Comparison (Current vs Previous Year) |
| 🥧 **Doughnut Chart** | Income Breakdown by Source |

**Chart Features:**
- Click-to-drill-down for detailed filtering
- Export as PNG images
- Responsive canvas sizing
- Custom color schemes

### 5️⃣ **Data Tables**

- **Recent Payments** — Last 20 transactions with full details
- **Unbalanced Loans** — Outstanding amounts with due dates
- **Unpaid Fees** — Members missing fee payments
- **Inventory Summary** — Stock levels with alerts

**Table Features:**
- Export to CSV
- Sortable columns
- Responsive design
- Visual status indicators

### 6️⃣ **Inventory Management**

- Item-wise stock tracking (IN/OUT/Balance)
- Low stock warnings (≤5 units)
- Out-of-stock alerts
- Visual stock level bars
- Automatic balance calculations

### 7️⃣ **Filters & Export**

- **Dynamic Filters:**
  - Year selection
  - Month filtering
  - Bank-specific views
  - Member filtering

- **Export Options:**
  - CSV export (all tables)
  - PNG export (charts)
  - Print-optimized layout
  - Batch export functionality

