## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Backend
- **PHP 8.0+** — Server-side logic
- **MySQL 8.0+** — Database management
- **AppGini Framework** — Rapid application development

### Frontend
- **HTML5 / CSS3** — Modern markup & styling
- **Bootstrap 5.3** — Responsive UI framework
- **JavaScript (ES6+)** — Interactive functionality
- **Chart.js 4.4** — Data visualization

### Design
- **Google Fonts** — Syne (headings) + DM Sans (body)
- **Bootstrap Icons** — Icon library
- **Custom CSS Variables** — Theming system
- **Dark Theme** — Professional executive aesthetic

### Features
- **Responsive Grid** — Mobile-first design
- **Intersection Observer** — Scroll animations
- **LocalStorage API** — Client-side caching
- **Fetch API** — AJAX operations

