## 🔒 Security

### Search Engine Protection

**Prevent Indexing:**
```html
<!-- Already included in dashboard.php -->
<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow, noarchive">
```

**HTTP Header:**
```php
header('X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow', true);
```

### Access Control

**Basic Authentication (.htaccess):**
```apache
AuthType Basic
AuthName "Restricted Area"
AuthUserFile /path/to/.htpasswd
Require valid-user
```

**IP Whitelist:**
```apache
Order Deny,Allow
Deny from all
Allow from 192.168.1.100
Allow from YOUR_IP_ADDRESS
```

### Best Practices

✅ **Use HTTPS** — Encrypt all traffic  
✅ **Session Management** — Implement timeouts  
✅ **SQL Injection Prevention** — Use prepared statements  
✅ **XSS Protection** — HTML escaping (`esc()` function)  
✅ **CSRF Tokens** — Validate form submissions  
✅ **Regular Backups** — Automated daily backups  
✅ **Access Logs** — Monitor dashboard access  
✅ **Strong Passwords** — Enforce password policies  

### robots.txt

Create in website root:
```txt
User-agent: *
Disallow: /dashboard.php
Disallow: /custom-pages/
Disallow: /*_view.php
```

