## 🗄 Database Schema

### Core Tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `loan_application` | Loan requests and approvals |
| `loan_repayment` | Payment transactions |
| `loan_fund` | Fund contributions |
| `members` | Member profiles |
| `member_fees` | Membership fee payments |
| `bank_data` | Bank deposits/withdrawals |
| `other_incame` | Other income sources |
| `expenses` | Expense tracking |
| `inventory` | Stock movements |
| `items` | Inventory items |

### Key Relationships

```
members
  ├─→ loan_application (Member_ID → Index)
  ├─→ loan_repayment (Member_ID → Index)
  ├─→ member_fees (Member_ID → Index)
  └─→ benefits (Member_ID → Index)

loan_application
  ├─→ loan_repayment (ID → Loan_application)
  └─→ approval (ID → Laon_application)

bank_names
  └─→ bank_data (ID → Bank)

income_types
  └─→ other_incame (Id → Income_type)

items
  └─→ inventory (ID → Items)
```

