## 📡 API Reference

### Helper Functions

```php
// Execute query and return all rows
q($conn, $sql) → array

// Execute query and return first row
q1($conn, $sql) → array

// Format currency (Rs. 1,234.56)
money($value) → string

// HTML escape for XSS protection
esc($value) → string

// Trend badge (↑ 15.2% or ↓ 8.3%)
trendBadge($current, $previous) → string
```

### JavaScript Functions

```javascript
// Toggle sidebar (mobile)
toggleSidebar()
closeSidebar()

// Export table to CSV
exportTableCSV(tableId, filename)

// Export chart as PNG
exportChart(canvasId, filename)

// Export all tables
exportAllCSV()

// Drill-down handler
drillDown(type, elements, chart)
```

